      <guid>//crypt0.net/daily/daily-trust-news-2017-04-02/</guid>
      <description>&lt;p&gt;Daily Security news from &lt;a href=&#34;http://twitter.com/trustpath&#34;&gt;@trustpath&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;h3&gt;SIEM Security: As Secure As It SIEMs&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;security can protect your business from dangerous threats without &amp;hellip;  &lt;a href=&#34;http://www.blackstratus.com/tag/security-event-management/&#34; onclick=&#34;trackOutboundLink(&#39;http://www.blackstratus.com/tag/security-event-management/&#39;); return false;&#34;&gt;more&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;h3&gt;SIEM Security: As Secure As It SIEMs&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;security can protect your business from dangerous threats without &amp;hellip;  &lt;a href=&#34;http://www.blackstratus.com/tag/security-information-management/&#34; onclick=&#34;trackOutboundLink(&#39;http://www.blackstratus.com/tag/security-information-management/&#39;); return false;&#34;&gt;more&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;h3&gt;Gemalto releases findings of 2016 Breach Level Index&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Gemalto released the findings of the 2016 Breach Level Index (BLI) revealing that Middle East data breaches are up 16.67 per cent compared to 2015.  &lt;a href=&#34;http://cpifinancial.net/news/post/40349/gemalto-releases-findings-of-2016-breach-level-index&#34; onclick=&#34;trackOutboundLink(&#39;http://cpifinancial.net/news/post/40349/gemalto-releases-findings-of-2016-breach-level-index&#39;); return false;&#34;&gt;more&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;h3&gt;Middle East data hacks on the rise, research shows&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The number of data breaches in the Middle East has risen 16.67 percent since 2015 as hackers become increasingly sophisticated, according to &amp;hellip;  &lt;a href=&#34;http://www.arabianbusiness.com/middle-east-data-hacks-on-rise-research-shows-669327.html&#34; onclick=&#34;trackOutboundLink(&#39;http://www.arabianbusiness.com/middle-east-data-hacks-on-rise-research-shows-669327.html&#39;); return false;&#34;&gt;more&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;h3&gt;Vantage point: Insights from cutting-edge research&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Gemalto, an international digital security company, has released the findings of the Breach Level Index. About 33 reported data breaches led to almost &amp;hellip;  &lt;a href=&#34;http://www.business-standard.com/article/companies/vantage-point-insights-from-cutting-edge-research-117040200732_1.html&#34; onclick=&#34;trackOutboundLink(&#39;http://www.business-standard.com/article/companies/vantage-point-insights-from-cutting-edge-research-117040200732_1.html&#39;); return false;&#34;&gt;more&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;h3&gt;More than 44 data records comprised every second in 2016 - digital security&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Irish Independent Global digital security company Gemalto&amp;rsquo;s 2016 Breach Level Index shows that 1,792 data breaches led to almost 1.4 billion data records being &amp;hellip;  &lt;a href=&#34;http://www.independent.ie/datasec/more-than-44-data-records-comprised-every-second-in-2016-digital-security-report-35587280.html&#34; onclick=&#34;trackOutboundLink(&#39;http://www.independent.ie/datasec/more-than-44-data-records-comprised-every-second-in-2016-digital-security-report-35587280.html&#39;); return false;&#34;&gt;more&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;h3&gt;Gemalto&amp;rsquo;s Breach Level Index: 1.4 billion compromised data records&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Gemalto released the results of its Breach Level Index last week, proving once again that data breaches across the world continue to increase in scale &amp;hellip;  &lt;a href=&#34;https://securitybrief.com.au/story/gemaltos-breach-level-index-14-billion-compromised-data-records/&#34; onclick=&#34;trackOutboundLink(&#39;https://securitybrief.com.au/story/gemaltos-breach-level-index-14-billion-compromised-data-records/&#39;); return false;&#34;&gt;more&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
</description>
